title: A Review of MMA 56 Brendan Schaub
description:
Brendan is a former UFC fighter and now a stand up comedian getting ready to release his new stand up comedy special on Showtime. He is also one of Joe Rogan’s best friends and host of the Fighter and the Kid podcast. He’s hilarious and always makes for a great conversation.

Enjoy my review folks!
